Okay, let's create a custom social share feature for your WordPress single posts, complete with a modal popup. This solution will use Vanilla JavaScript, CSS, and some basic HTML, integrated into your WordPress theme.

**Goal:**

*   A share icon appears on single posts.
*   Clicking the icon opens a modal popup.
*   The modal contains "Share This Post" title.
*   It has buttons for Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, WhatsApp, and Copy Link.
*   These buttons share the *current post's* URL and title.
*   The "Copy Link" button copies the current post's URL to the clipboard.
*   The modal can be closed by clicking outside it, or by clicking a close button.

---

### Step 1: Enqueue Styles and Scripts (functions.php)

You'll need to enqueue a Font Awesome stylesheet for the icons, your custom CSS, and your custom JavaScript file.

Open your theme's `functions.php` file (or preferably, your child theme's `functions.php`). Add the following code:

```php
<?php
/**
 * Enqueue custom social share scripts and styles.
 */
function mytheme_enqueue_social_share_assets() {
    // Enqueue Font Awesome (if your theme doesn't already)
    wp_enqueue_style( 'font-awesome-all', 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css', array(), '6.0.0-beta3', 'all' );

    // Enqueue custom social share CSS
    wp_enqueue_style( 'mytheme-social-share-style', get_stylesheet_directory_uri() . '/css/social-share.css', array(), '1.0.0', 'all' );

    // Enqueue custom social share JavaScript
    wp_enqueue_script( 'mytheme-social-share-script', get_stylesheet_directory_uri() . '/js/social-share.js', array(), '1.0.0', true ); // true loads script in footer
}
add_action( 'wp_enqueue_scripts', 'mytheme_enqueue_social_share_assets' );

?>
```

**Explanation:**

*   `mytheme_enqueue_social_share_assets()`: This function will register and load our necessary files.
*   `wp_enqueue_style('font-awesome-all', ...)`: Loads Font Awesome from a CDN. If your theme already loads Font Awesome, you can skip this line.
*   `wp_enqueue_style('mytheme-social-share-style', ...)`: Loads your custom CSS file. We'll create this at `your-theme/css/social-share.css`.
*   `wp_enqueue_script('mytheme-social-share-script', ...)`: Loads your custom JavaScript file. We'll create this at `your-theme/js/social-share.js`. The `true` argument ensures it loads in the footer, which is good practice.
*   `add_action('wp_enqueue_scripts', ...)`: Hooks our function into WordPress's script/style loading process.

---

### Step 2: Create CSS File (`css/social-share.css`)

Create a new directory named `css` inside your theme's root folder (or child theme's root folder). Inside `css`, create a file named `social-share.css` and add the following styles:

```css
/* Share Button */
.custom-share-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background-color: #0073aa; /* WordPress blue */
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 20px; /* Adjust as needed */
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.custom-share-button:hover {
    background-color: #005177;
}

.custom-share-button i {
    font-size: 18px;
}

/* Modal Overlay */
.share-modal-overlay {
    display: none; /* Hidden by default */
    position: fixed; /* Stay in place */
    z-index: 9999; /* Sit on top */
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%; /* Full width */
    height: 100%; /* Full height */
    overflow: auto; /* Enable scroll if needed */
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* Black w/ opacity */
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Modal Content */
.share-modal-content {
    background-color: #fefefe;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    width: 90%; /* Adjust width for responsiveness */
    max-width: 500px; /* Max width for larger screens */
    animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-20px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

/* Close Button */
.share-modal-close {
    color: #aaa;
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    right: 15px;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.share-modal-close:hover,
.share-modal-close:focus {
    color: #333;
    text-decoration: none;
}

/* Modal Title */
.share-modal-content h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 15px;
}

/* Social Buttons Container */
.share-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow buttons to wrap on smaller screens */
    gap: 15px; /* Spacing between buttons */
    justify-content: center;
}

/* Individual Social Button */
.share-buttons a,
.share-buttons button {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%; /* Full width on small screens */
    max-width: 220px; /* Max width for larger screens */
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.share-buttons a:hover,
.share-buttons button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.share-buttons a i,
.share-buttons button i {
    margin-right: 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
}

/* Specific Social Colors */
.share-facebook {
    background-color: #1877f2;
}
.share-twitter {
    background-color: #1da1f2;
}
.share-linkedin {
    background-color: #0a66c2;
}
.share-whatsapp {
    background-color: #25d366;
}
.share-copylink {
    background-color: #6c757d; /* Bootstrap secondary grey */
}

/* Copy Link confirmation message */
.copy-message {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #28a745; /* Green success color */
    opacity: 0; /* Hidden by default */
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;
}
.copy-message.show {
    opacity: 1;
}

/* Hidden input for copying */
.hidden-url-input {
    position: absolute;
    left: -9999px;
}

/* Responsive Adjustments */
@media (min-width: 576px) {
    .share-buttons {
        justify-content: space-between; /* Evenly space buttons */
    }
    .share-buttons a,
    .share-buttons button {
        width: calc(50% - 10px); /* Two columns with gap */
    }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .share-modal-content {
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .share-modal-content h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .share-buttons a,
    .share-buttons button {
        font-size: 15px;
        padding: 10px 15px;
    }
}
```

